{"tid":85854,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴絲鍾意話劇/舞台呢類？","createTime":"2017-01-18T15:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T11:43:09.000Z","uid":77383,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"15bb796f6b0e78e9bbd843345c6f8b670209ad99","tid":85854,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:33:27.000Z","msg":"見到有好多人都淨係鍾意睇電視電影聽音樂，我想問下有冇人鍾意舞台劇？或者係做呢一行？唔一定只係話劇，可以係演唱會，DJ Show之類台燈聲既人。<br />\n一直發現都冇咩巴絲會討論，唔知可唔可以搵到同好一齊討論舞台劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由中四開始接觸舞台一直都好鍾意所以DSE後就去左讀有關既課程，但因為讀既人少識既人唔多，有時想睇啲劇都冇人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想係呢方面識多啲人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲係演員就快出show要人黎撐場呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小妹得閒會黎睇架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a323c4f9e532f1c90a27522a78aff388c275cc63","tid":85854,"uid":16577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:41:13.000Z","msg":"做緊聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  望住人咁重既喇叭吊上天 好爽"},{"pid":"6b8d8298e4a91817ca6a1f8a5994e80d2d93e2d4","tid":85854,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:44:38.000Z","msg":"我以前睇過一套話劇個名係巴士號碼黎(唔記得乜名)，講個巴士司機要自殺，決定係天橋個位衝出去。<br />\n呢套野係業餘演員演出既，不過令我震撼左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人都睇過？？"},{"pid":"3a86b77bc17b6d3f518768c4089f99f40c7ee52f","tid":85854,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:46:07.000Z","msg":"劇組係戲同行黎，唔係太出名<br />\n不過我每套都有支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27a86b83d5d21b75eecf8ad57d2a7e1dfd7511f6","tid":85854,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做緊聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  望住人咁重既喇叭吊上天 好爽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有次跟show隻Meyer喇叭跌左落地"},{"pid":"3f956cd33e1e26110ebad690580762fc92cf94ea","tid":85854,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T15:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我以前睇過一套話劇個名係巴士號碼黎(唔記得乜名)，講個巴士司機要自殺，決定係天橋個位衝出去。<br />\n呢套野係業餘演員演出既，不過令我震撼左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人都睇過？？</blockquote><br />\n有時覺得舞台劇個珍貴位係唔一定套套都會拍片backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   以後想回顧下到無，靠回憶"},{"pid":"cdaadfbcf9e590acedd69db5163573791ea9a35f","tid":85854,"uid":66236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:00:30.000Z","msg":"LM<br />\n好鍾意風車草"},{"pid":"9505658b3ab2b5b7bb2334add6424c4457a06072","tid":85854,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:01:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我以前睇過一套話劇個名係巴士號碼黎(唔記得乜名)，講個巴士司機要自殺，決定係天橋個位衝出去。<br />\n呢套野係業餘演員演出既，不過令我震撼左幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人都睇過？？</blockquote><br />\n有時覺得舞台劇個珍貴位係唔一定套套都會拍片backup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   以後想回顧下到無，靠回憶</blockquote><br />\n係，呢套劇完左之後只存在係我記憶<br />\n呢套劇精彩到我覺得可以拍成電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2c6f01949b960d889b8aa1a6a08dce516ae6830","tid":85854,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>LM<br />\n好鍾意風車草</blockquote><br />\n黎緊風車草 3月有套「你咪理&middot;我愛你」（好似係咁既名）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有蝦頭同梁祖堯睇"},{"pid":"869adea076ff630ec2c1228fa887d0ea26d0f6fb","tid":85854,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T16:07:28.000Z","msg":"睇一場其實好貴<br />\n<br />\n利申:做過幾次LIGHTING"},{"pid":"1e6d3100f212c3f0f177158e5fdc37ef02d37b05","tid":85854,"uid":66236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T17:12:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>LM<br />\n好鍾意風車草</blockquote><br />\n黎緊風車草 3月有套「你咪理&middot;我愛你」（好似係咁既名）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有蝦頭同梁祖堯睇</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [black]今日公開發售<br />\n飛已買[/black]"},{"pid":"57e7051af428dd51b3a607d70f0b2f8cd8dec6fe","tid":85854,"uid":16577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:45:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做緊聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  望住人咁重既喇叭吊上天 好爽</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有次跟show隻Meyer喇叭跌左落地</blockquote><br />\n隨時dup親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0625af1a03e25a40c17ae6dbb691c7c3d839d56c","tid":85854,"uid":53607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T05:52:48.000Z","msg":"有,粵劇都有"},{"pid":"f337dc5ca391b9d2cd5b06c0d35d902b7b81f622","tid":85854,"uid":35193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T06:47:47.000Z","msg":"鍾意自己做多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4adcbb849754aa667089d62e8b6cc5070103cd03","tid":85854,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:03:21.000Z","msg":"以前中學成日被迫睇<br />\n麻麻哋舞台劇"},{"pid":"4bb25dff58961489381bf94f0c9898570aa84b0c","tid":85854,"uid":10874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T09:18:55.000Z","msg":"組返隊連登劇團 我第一個參加"},{"pid":"9e2a48357d78a39b79201afaaa997aac156cc6cf","tid":85854,"uid":77383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-19T10:11:59.000Z